"FEM Mesh with Results — $Mesh

"Simple 2D mesh: 4 nodes, 2 triangles
x_n = [0; 2; 2; 0]
y_n = [0; 0; 2; 2]

"Elements (triangles: 3 nodes each)
e = [1; 2; 3 | 1; 3; 4]

"Supports (node; direction)
s = [1; 1 | 1; 2 | 4; 1]

"Forces (node; direction; value)
f = [2; 1; 10 | 3; 2; -5]

"SVG Mesh with supports and loads
$Mesh{x_n; y_n; e; s; f @ w = 400}

"Stress results per element
sigma = [150; 85]

"Color-mapped results
$MeshResults{x_n; y_n; e; sigma @ w = 400}
